name: The Queen's Dreams: Born Again
description:
The Sun rose and shone on the glistening waters.
The jarring impact had caused fissures in the ground that sprung crystals and vapours that intoxicated the nose and the mind.
The air was deep and thick.
A calm after a shoulder sobbing cry.
A hopeful tint to the air.
The madness had stopped.
The chaos was over.
She had burned through to the embers and was now living through the crisp morning dew after the fog.
